These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, fanta, water, iced-tea
The people have 4 different hobbies: writing, chess, collecting, card-games
1. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking coffee and the person who's hobby is chess##2
2. the person drinking fanta is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is writing##3
3. the person drinking fanta is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking coffee##7
4. the person who's hobby is chess is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
6. the person who's hobby is chess is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is writing##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |       3       |      4      |
| Beverage   | water | iced-tea       | fanta | coffee        |
| Hobby      | collecting  | chess | card-games        | writing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-2::.
4 different pets are kept: ferret, fish, chinchilla, guinea-pig
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: handball, sailing, cricket, golf
1. the person who's sport is golf is somewhere between the person who's sport is cricket and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is golf##5
4. the owner of the fish is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person who's sport is sailing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |     2      |       3       |    4    |
| Pet     | chinchilla | fish       | guinea-pig         | ferret     |
| Sport   | sailing   | golf | cricket | handball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, superhero, satire, western
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: hip-hop, electronic, d&b, salsa
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the fan of salsa##1
2. the fan of salsa is somewhere between the fan of electronic and the fan of hip-hop##7
3. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
4. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere between the fan of salsa and the person watching superhero movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |    3    |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | superhero | western | satire | martial-arts  |
| Music-Genre   | d&b | hip-hop  | salsa   | electronic |

