.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, fishing, filmmaking, camping
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, baseball, cricket, swimming
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left or far right##3
2. the person who's hobby is baking is somewhere between the person who's sport is baseball and the person who's hobby is camping##7
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is the person who's sport is swimming##1
4. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
5. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |     2      |       3       |      4      |
| Hobby   | fishing | baking | camping       | filmmaking |
| Sport   | baseball      | ice-hockey   | cricket | swimming  |

