.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-5::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, fishing, hiking, singing
There are 4 different nationalities: indonesian, turkish, russian, nigerian
1. the nigerian is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is fishing##3
2. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the turkish##5
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
4. the nigerian is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
5. the nigerian is on the left of the russian##1
6. the turkish is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
7. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the far left or far right##3
8. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is hiking##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Hobby         | hiking | cooking   | singing | fishing |
| Nationality   | indonesian      | turkish | nigerian      | russian |

