.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-6::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, iced-tea, soy-milk, cola
There are 4 different nationalities: german, turkish, british, italian
1. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the british##1
2. the british is the person drinking cola##1
3. the turkish is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left or right of the italian##3
6. the italian is somewhere between the german and the turkish##7
7. the british is somewhere to the right of the person drinking soy-milk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | lemonade      | soy-milk | cola     |
| Nationality   | german    | italian | turkish   | british |

