.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-7::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, lime, cranberry, apricot
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, indian, indonesian, malaysian
1. the brazilian is on the far left##1
2. the person eating lime is on the left of the indian##1
3. the person eating apricot is on the far left or far right##3
4. the malaysian is somewhere between the person eating tomato and the person eating cranberry##7
5. the indonesian is somewhere to the left of the person eating cranberry##5
6. the malaysian is on the left or right of the indonesian##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food          | apricot    | tomato   | lime | cranberry  |
| Nationality   | brazilian | indonesian | malaysian    | indian |

