.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-8::.
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, canadian, russian, brazilian
4 different pets are kept: hedgehog, guinea-pig, mouse, lizard
1. the canadian is not the owner of the lizard##6
2. the owner of the mouse is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
3. the brazilian is the owner of the mouse##1
4. the russian is somewhere between the brazilian and the thai##7
5. the canadian is on the left of the thai##1
6. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
7. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |     3     |    4     |
| Nationality   | brazilian | russian | canadian | thai |
| Pet           | mouse   | lizard    | hedgehog       | guinea-pig  |

