.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-9::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, project-manager, journalist, accountant
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, soul, house, indie
1. the librarian is not the fan of folk##6
2. the journalist is on the right of the librarian##1
3. the fan of folk is on the left or right of the librarian##3
4. the librarian is on the right of the fan of indie##1
5. the journalist is somewhere between the fan of indie and the project-manager##7
6. the fan of soul is somewhere to the right of the fan of house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |       4        |
| Job           | accountant | librarian | journalist | project-manager |
| Music-Genre   | indie         | house      | folk | soul            |

