.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-10::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: horror, musical, romance, superhero
4 different pets are kept: goat, bird, turtle, fish
1. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere between the person watching horror movies and the owner of the fish##7
2. the person watching musical movies is not the owner of the turtle##6
3. the owner of the bird is not the person watching romance movies##6
4. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the fish##5
5. the person watching horror movies is the owner of the goat##1
6. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the right of the owner of the goat##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Movie-Genre   | horror | superhero | musical | romance |
| Pet           | goat    | bird   | fish  | turtle      |

