.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-11::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: thriller, scientific, spy, family
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, classical, reggae, hip-hop
1. the fan of hip-hop is somewhere to the right of the fan of salsa##5
2. the fan of reggae is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of classical is somewhere to the left of the person watching spy movies##5
4. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching thriller movies is between the person watching scientific movies and the fan of classical##2
6. the fan of reggae is somewhere between the fan of classical and the person watching scientific movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |      3      |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | family | thriller | scientific | spy   |
| Music-Genre   | classical    | reggae      | salsa      | hip-hop |

