3. the person who's sport is parkour is not the person who's hobby is fishing##6
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
6. the person who's hobby is drawing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is fishing and the person who's hobby is skydiving##7

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2      |      3      |    4    |
