.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, puzzles, sudoku
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, jet-ski, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
2. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the person driving the van##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is puzzles##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is not the person driving the jet-ski##6
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
6. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the person driving the van and the person who's hobby is puzzles##7
7. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the left of the person driving the skateboard##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Hobby       | sudoku | rock-climbing | singing | puzzles |
| Transport   | van   | snowmobile      | jet-ski        | skateboard  |

