The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, soul, jazz, punk
1. the fan of soul is in an even position##4
2. the fan of punk is somewhere between the person drinking tea and the fan of jazz##7
3. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
4. the fan of jazz is in an even position##4
5. the person drinking soy-milk is somewhere to the left of the fan of soul##5
6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
7. the person drinking juice is the fan of punk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |   3   |    4    |
| Beverage      | soy-milk   | milk | juice | tea   |
| Music-Genre   | rock | jazz   | punk | soul |

