.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-7-20::.
4 different pets are kept: mouse, chinchilla, rat, guinea-pig
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, tram, ship
1. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the bike and the owner of the chinchilla##7
2. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the boat##1
3. the owner of the guinea-pig is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the person driving the boat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
5. the owner of the rat is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2     |     3     |  4  |
| Pet         | chinchilla    | rat | guinea-pig     | mouse |
| Transport   | tram | ship  | boat | bike |

 